{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285550/extras/\u82f1\u6587\u52a0\u613f\u671b\u5355.gif?t=1738721760\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embark on a journey to Doloc Town, a post-apocalyptic oasis filled with abandoned ruins, unique architecture and warm-hearted people.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285550/extras/Visual.gif?t=1738721760\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Build your farm and get to know the stories of this forgotten land. Thrive and discover your destiny as you explore deeper into this unknown territory!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285550/extras/\u591a\u6d1b\u514b_\u5c0f\u6807\u9898-\u6a21\u62df\u7ecf\u8425_1_.png?t=1738721760\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285550/extras/Farming.gif?t=1738721760\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gather resources to get your farm started. As a farmer, you're tasked with planting, watering, harvesting, and even shielding crops from adverse weather.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Construct buildings, upgrade facilities, and craft advanced tools to turn your little corner into a farming paradise!<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285550/extras/\u591a\u6d1b\u514b_\u5c0f\u6807\u9898-\u63a2\u7d22_1_.png?t=1738721760\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285550/extras/Explore.gif?t=1738721760\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore this unknown terorritory, with intricate valley, treacherous wetland and abanoned ruins awaits. Scout the vast, untouched wilderness in search for secret relics &amp; treasures and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">At the center of the map lies Doloc Town, a post-apocalyptic sanctuary built from the debris of trains and bridge structures. Get to know the townsfolk and connect with them for much-needed resources. Have a drink with villagers to discover their stories and unfold the hidden secrets of this land. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Above all, the key is to endure the wasteland and pursue whatever your heart truly desires.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285550/extras/\u591a\u6d1b\u514b_\u5c0f\u6807\u9898-\u6218\u6597_1_.png?t=1738721760\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285550/extras/Combat.gif?t=1738721760\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock your drone companion and enjoy fast-paced bullet hell combat! Shoot, refill, and dodge your way through this unknown wilderness. Upgrade &amp; modify your weaponry to fit various combat needs. Slay dangerous creatures and face ever stronger enemies encountered along the way!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285550/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738721760","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285550/page.bg.jpg?t=1738721760","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285550/f56da64cc29e6fcc12223361a81226ea2928af6b/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738721760","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285550/f56da64cc29e6fcc12223361a81226ea2928af6b/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738721760","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","demos":[{"appid":3243760,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<h1>Join Our Community!</h1><p><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285550/extras/\u591a\u6d1b\u53efdiscord\u56fe600x125.png?t=1738721760\" /></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285550/extras/\u82f1\u6587\u52a0\u613f\u671b\u5355.gif?t=1738721760\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embark on a journey to Doloc Town, a post-apocalyptic oasis filled with abandoned ruins, unique architecture and warm-hearted people.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285550/extras/Visual.gif?t=1738721760\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Build your farm and get to know the stories of this forgotten land. Thrive and discover your destiny as you explore deeper into this unknown territory!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285550/extras/\u591a\u6d1b\u514b_\u5c0f\u6807\u9898-\u6a21\u62df\u7ecf\u8425_1_.png?t=1738721760\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285550/extras/Farming.gif?t=1738721760\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gather resources to get your farm started. As a farmer, you're tasked with planting, watering, harvesting, and even shielding crops from adverse weather.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Construct buildings, upgrade facilities, and craft advanced tools to turn your little corner into a farming paradise!<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285550/extras/\u591a\u6d1b\u514b_\u5c0f\u6807\u9898-\u63a2\u7d22_1_.png?t=1738721760\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285550/extras/Explore.gif?t=1738721760\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore this unknown terorritory, with intricate valley, treacherous wetland and abanoned ruins awaits. Scout the vast, untouched wilderness in search for secret relics &amp; treasures and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">At the center of the map lies Doloc Town, a post-apocalyptic sanctuary built from the debris of trains and bridge structures. Get to know the townsfolk and connect with them for much-needed resources. Have a drink with villagers to discover their stories and unfold the hidden secrets of this land. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Above all, the key is to endure the wasteland and pursue whatever your heart truly desires.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285550/extras/\u591a\u6d1b\u514b_\u5c0f\u6807\u9898-\u6218\u6597_1_.png?t=1738721760\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285550/extras/Combat.gif?t=1738721760\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock your drone companion and enjoy fast-paced bullet hell combat! Shoot, refill, and dodge your way through this unknown wilderness. Upgrade &amp; modify your weaponry to fit various combat needs. Slay dangerous creatures and face ever stronger enemies encountered along the way!</p>","developers":["RedSaw Games Studio"],"genres":[{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"},{"description":"Simulation","id":"28"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285550/header.jpg?t=1738721760","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257067934,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257067934/movie480.mp4?t=1730185025","max":